channel.title: ASF JIRA
channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HBASE-11583] Refactoring out the configuration changes for enabling VisibilityLabels in the unit tests.
item.description: All the unit tests contain the code for enabling the visibility changes. Incorporating future configuration changes for Visibility Labels configuration can be made easier by refactoring them out to a single place.
item.summary: Refactoring out the configuration changes for enabling VisibilityLabels in the unit tests.

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.
